ActVisiting Forces Act
Revised Statutes of Canada, 1985 Act
SubjectAmendment to a Proclamation under the Visiting Forces Act for the Republic of North Macedonia
PrecisOrder amending the PROCLAMATION DESIGNATING CERTAIN COUNTRIES AS DESIGNATED STATES for the purposes of the Visiting Forces Act in order to replace “former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia” with its new official name of "the Republic of North Macedonia."
